{"name":"Heather Mason","nameCn":"海瑟·梅森","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/13/ed/21817_crt_3L773.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>海瑟·梅森</li><li><span>别名: </span>希瑟·茉莉丝（Heather Moris）</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>希瑟·梅森</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Heather Mason</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ヘザー</li><li><span>性别: </span>女</li><li><span>年龄: </span>17</li>","detail":"故事的主角。个性有些暴躁易怒，似乎不管在哪里都存在的少女类型。在某个星期日，海瑟在购物中心逛街时莫名其妙被卷入了异世界。对于异常事态，虽然感到害怕但也拥有正面对抗的勇气。<br />真实身分为一代主角哈利‧梅森从寂静岭抱回来的女孩，也就是亚雷莎与雪柔的共同体，“海瑟”是她的假名。<br />顺带一提，在某些海外版本，名字为“海瑟·茉莉丝（Heather Moris）”。这是因为实际上，担任主角海瑟的配音与行动模组的女演员，名字就叫做海瑟·茉莉丝，日本版并没有记载“Moris”这个名字。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/3775","name":"サイレントヒル3","nameCn":"寂静岭3","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/f2/b9/3775_2gWwG.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"Heather Morris","castHref":"/person/35034","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/0e/63/35034_prsn_ry6R8.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/53665","name":"Silent Hill: Book of Memories","nameCn":"寂静岭：记忆之书","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/c7/e7/53665_pl66o.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"Amanda Winn-Lee","castHref":"/person/35035","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/43/c9/35035_prsn_MdW1u.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/41545","name":"サイレントヒル ダウンプア","nameCn":"寂静岭 暴雨","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/db/86/41545_GGdd4.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/3771","name":"サイレントヒル","nameCn":"寂静岭","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/20/1e/3771_R6drs.jpg","staff":"客串","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""}]}